<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "profile_image.jpg", width: 250, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div 
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                >   
                </div>
              </div>
            </div> 
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>The need for a bigger purpose and the desire for a better future pushed me to pursue software development. I wanted to attain a specific skill set that people need in the world today. When my baseball career came to an end, I needed something to fill that enormous hole. Becoming a software developer did exactly that.</p>

        <p> I am currently enrolled at Bottega Tech where I am learning Ruby on Rails, HTML, CSS and Javascript as well as SQL. It is my goal to become a highly successful Ruby developer. I love what I am learning and am eager to join the development community.</p>

        
        <button
          class="btn btn-primary"
          type="button"
          data-toggle="collapse"
          data-target="#jobHistory"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-controler="jobHistory"
        >
          Job History
        </button>

        <button
          class="btn btn-primary"
          type="button"
          data-toggle="collapse"
          data-target="#education"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-controler="education"
        >
          Education
        </button>
      

        <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
          <div class="card card-block">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-3">
                <%= image_tag "relevant.png", width: '100%', alt: "Relevant Inc.", class: 'relevant-logo' %>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-9">
                Junior Software Developer
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="collapse" id="education">
          <div class="card card-block">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-3">
                <%= image_tag "bottega.jpg", width: '100%', alt: "Bottega", class: 'bottega-logo' %>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-9">
                Currently enrolled at Bottega Tech studying Ruby on Rails development.  
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card card-block">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-3">
                <%= image_tag "uvu.png", width: '100%', alt: "UVU", class: 'uvu-logo' %>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-9">
                Graduated from Utah Valley University in 2017 with a BS in Public Relations. 
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card card-block">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-3">
                <%= image_tag "slcc.png", width: '100%', alt: "SLCC", class: 'slcc-logo' %>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-9">
                Graduated from Salt Lake Community College in 2015 with an Associates of Science. 
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>




